    "EBM-NLP dataset 13 developed by Nye et al. (2018) is the only readily available dataset with explicitly recognised PICO elements.",
    "This dataset contains approximately 4993 annotated abstracts of PICO elements of medical journals outlining clinical trials.",
    "Since the annotation of the PICO is done on the abstract and not in full text, challenges may arise for journals with the PICO elements in the full text.",
